Given a grid with Red and Green cells,
always flip the top left corner one from R to G or from G to R.
Every time, you can flip the top left corner one with all its same color connected neighbors.
Question, how many times to flip all to a same color.

RG
GR

to

GG
GR

to

RR
RR

Answer: 2

---

RRR
GRR

to

GGG
GGG

Answer: 1


